window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Thirty and single? Well, getcha butt to the Gathering! </p> <p>As if hitting 30 wasn't enough, unmated Scarlet Wickham is summoned to this year's Gathering. As a woman marked to be the mate of an Alpha pair, she's not going to find happiness anywhere other than in the arms of two Alpha werewolves. So, off she goes with her sisters in tow. 'Cause yeah, she's one of the plump Wickham triplets, and they're all being carted off to werewolf speed dating. </p> <p>Keller and Madden, ruling Alpha pair, can't believe their luck. They've found their mate, and she's more than they could have ever hoped for. She's feisty with spirit to spare, and lush curves that they want to trace with their tongues. They can't wait to solidify their bond and get to know the beautiful woman who is to rule at their side. But first, there's the minor inconvenience of a challenge to the death.... </p>"; 
